articles.author: Angus Watson, Lizzy Yee, Tara Subramaniam
articles.title: Surfer fights for his life after shark attack in Australia - CNN
articles.description: A surfer is fighting for his life in the hospital after he was attacked by a shark off Australia’s east coast, police said Friday.
articles.content:
A surfer is fighting for his life in the hospital after he was attacked by a shark off Australias east coast, police said Friday.
